cluding%20their%20carry-on%20baggage%2C%20for%20domestic%20flights%20from%20Gimpo%20Airport%20from%20August%2028%20to%20September%206%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkoreajoongangdaily.joins.com%2Fnews%2F2023-08-21%2Fbusiness%2Findustry%2FKorean-Air-faces-backlash-over-move-to-weigh-passengers%2F1851432%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Korea%20JoongAng%20Daily.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20international%20flights%20out%20of%20Incheon%20Airport%2C%20passengers%20will%20be%20weighed%20from%20September%208%20to%2019%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider%2C%20the%20airline%20said%20other%20Korean%20carriers%20would%20have%20to%20do%20something%20similar%20in%20order%20to%20supply%20data%20required%20by%20Korea's%20Ministry%20of%20Land%2C%20Infrastructure%20and%20Transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKorea%20JoongAng%20Daily%20reported%20that%20the%20airline%20told%20it%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20data%20collated%20anonymously%20will%20be%20utilized%20for%20survey%20purposes%20and%20doesn't%20mean%20overweight%20passengers%20will%20need%20to%20pay%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20weigh%20passengers%20is%20in%20response%20to%20a%20rule%20set%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Land%2C%20Infrastructure%2C%20and%20Transport%2C%20which%20mandates%20that%20airlines%20assess%20standardized%20passenger%20weights%20that%20include%20their%20carry-on%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20regulation%20means%20that%20airlines%20must%20calculate%20the%20standard%20weight%20of%20passengers%20at%20least%20every%20five%20years%20in%20order%20to%20work%20out%20how%20best%20to%20distribute%20aircraft%20weight%2C%20curtail%20fuel%20consumption%2C%20and%20enhance%20overall%20flight%20safety%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Korea%20JoongAng%20Daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20survey%2C%20conducted%20in%202017%2C%20found%20that%20the%20average%20weight%20for%20adult%20men%20during%20the%20summer%20season%20was%20178.6%20pounds%20and%20152.1%20pounds%20for%20women%2C%20per%20the%20Korean%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weighing%20will%20take%20place%20in%20front%20of%20the%20gates%20and%20before%20boarding%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreatimes.co.kr%2Fwww%2Ftech%2F2023%2F08%2F129_357431.html%5C%22%3EThe%20Korea%20Times%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20an%20online%20backlash%20to%20the%20measure%2C%20with%20some%20potential%20passengers%20raising%20concerns%20about%20their%20privacy%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Korea%20JoongAng%20Daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20airline%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20passengers%20who%20feel%20uncomfortable%20with%20the%20process%20can%20communicate%20their%20feelings%20to%20boarding%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20industry%20experts%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-check-ins-weight-watchers-scenario-customers-says-experts-2021-6%5C%22%3EInsider%20in%20June%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20US%20airlines%20are%20unlikely%20to%20do%20the%20same%2C%20with%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Authority%20currently%20allowing%20operators%20to%20ask%20passengers%20to%20volunteer%20their%20weight%20and%20%26quot%3Bmake%20a%20reasonable%20estimate%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20answer%20appears%20too%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20New%20Zealand%2C%20however%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-new-zealand-weigh-passengers-before-boarding-2023-5%5C%22%3Easking%20passengers%20to%20step%20on%20the%20scale%3C%2Fa%3Es%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpassenger%20weight%20survey%26quot%3B%20to%20fulfill%20a%20requirement%20by%20New%20Zealand's%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-airline-weigh-passengers-scales-boarding-gates-before-flights-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%2