C2%A0%20Schools%20are%20open%20and%20space%20enthusiasts%20are%20organising%20parties%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20historic%20moment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20moon%20lander%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2014%2C%20perched%20on%20a%20LVM%203%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle.%20It%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20lunar%20orbit%20on%20August%205.%20The%20lander%20Vikram%20is%20named%20after%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%2C%20who%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20programme.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20moon%20mission%2C%20ISRO%20has%20a%20number%20of%20projects%20lined%20up%20-%20one%20of%20them%20a%20mission%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%2C%20and%20a%20human%20space%20flight%20programme%2C%20Gaganyaan.%20Aditya-L1%2C%20the%20first%20space-based%20Indian%20observatory%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%2C%20is%20getting%20ready%20for%20the%20launch%2C%20most%20likely%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20September.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692795780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F25e4m4co_chandrayaan3-descent-isro-650_650x400_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lands-on-moon-india-joins-elite-space-club-4322798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20moon%20mission%20Chandrayaan-3%20has%20made%20a%20successful%20soft%20landing%20near%20the%20moon's%20South%20Pole%2C%20bringing%20cheer%20to%20a%20billion%20hearts%20and%20propelling%20India%20to%20the%20elite%20space%20club.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lands-on-moon-india-joins-elite-space-club-4322798%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lands-on-moon-india-joins-elite-space-club-4322798%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lands-on-moon-india-joins-elit