e%20main%20effort%20and%20avoiding%20allowing%20the%20enemy%20to%20concentrate%20all%20reserves%20on%20stopping%20a%20single%20obvious%20thrust.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%20Ukraine%20has%20been%20fighting%20a%20grueling%20counteroffensive%2C%20trying%20to%20breach%20Russian%20positions%20defended%20by%20miles%20of%20mines%2C%20and%20protected%20by%20heavy%20artillery%20fire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20Ukraine%20struggles%20to%20make%20a%20decisive%20breakthrough%2C%20differences%20are%20emerging%20with%20Western%20allies%20over%20the%20tactics%20it's%20using.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20abandoned%20some%20of%20the%20large-scale%20frontal%20attack%20plans%20its%20forces%20were%20trained%20to%20use%20when%20they%20didn't%20achieve%20a%20decisive%20breakthrough%2C%20and%20some%20Western%20equipment%20has%20proved%20ineffective%20at%20breaching%20Russian%20lines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20core%20aim%20of%20the%20counteroffensive%20is%20to%20cut%20off%20Russian%20supply%20routes%20between%20Russia%20and%20occupied%20Crimea.%20US%20and%20other%20Western%20officials%20told%20the%20Times%20that%20Ukraine%20is%20focusing%20too%20many%20forces%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20Bakhmut%2C%20and%20not%20enough%20on%20the%20southern%20front%20that%20they%20say%20should%20be%20the%20main%20focus%20of%20the%20counteroffensive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20analysts%20believe%20that%20Ukraine%20has%20to%20achieve%20a%20decisive%20breakthrough%20in%20its%20counteroffensive%20soon%2C%20as%20a%20protracted%20conflict%20would%20be%20to%20Russia's%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVitaliy%20Kryukov%2C%20a%20loitering-munition%20commander%20for%20the%20elite%20Adam%20Tactical%20Group%20previously%20told%20Insider's%20Sinead%20Baker%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-soldiers-reject-criticism-of-slow-advance-citing-russia-defenses-2023-8%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3EUkraine%20has%20to%20pick%20tactics%20that%20save%20as%20many%20of%2