he%20country%20is%20sensitive%20to.%20Filmmakers%20now%20have%20a%20legal%20department%20who%20will%20tell%20you%20not%20to%20go%20down%20a%20certain%20path.%20So%20there's%20check%20and%20balance%20happening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20during%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dyl0kDdh1OkY%5C%22%3ESucharita%20Tyagi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Karan%20Johar%20opened%20up%20about%20how%20he%20dealt%20with%20trolls%20and%20how%20it%20affected%20his%20mother%20Hiroo%20Johar.%20The%20filmmaker%20also%20confessed%20that%20he%20is%20now%20comfortable%20in%20his%20skin%20and%20he%20%26quot%3Bhas%20nothing%20to%20lose%20anymore%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaran%20Johar%20told%20Sucharita%20Tyagi%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20I%20felt%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20hate%20that%20was%20coming%20my%20way%20and%20it%20had%20really%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20my%20mom.%20I%20saw%20her%20literally%20crumble%20under%20that%20because%20she%20used%20to%20watch%20TV%20channels.%20She%20was%20reading%20stuff%20online.%20She%20was%20watching%20TV%20anchors%20screaming%20and%20shouting%20and%20saying%20the%20most%20godawful%20things%2C%20demonising%20me%20for%20some%20reason.%20Then%20there%20were%20people%20who%20were%20kind%20of%20writing%20the%20same%20on%20Twitter%20and%20other%20social%20media%20platforms.%26quot%3B%20Amid%20backlash%20and%20hate%2C%20Karan%20Johar%20quit%20Twitter%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaran%20Johar%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20director's%20seat%20after%20seven%20years%20with%20%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani.%3C%2Fem%3E%20His%20last%20directorial%20was%20%3Cem%3EAe%20Dil%20Hai%20Mushkil%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Karan%20Johar%20has%20directed%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3EKuch%20Kuch%20Hota%20Hai%2C%20Kabhi%20Khushi%20Kabhi%20Gham%2C%20My%20Name%20Is%20Khan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Karan%20Johar%20also%20completed%2025%20years%20as%20a%20director%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publ