the%20lander%2C%20but%20nothing%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20stated%20that%20the%20lander%20made%20a%20hard%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spacecraft%20successfully%20entered%20the%20lunar%20orbit%20on%20August%2020%20by%20performing%20Lunar%20Orbit%20Insertion%20(LOI)%20manoeuvre%2C%20and%20on%20September%202%2C%20''Vikram''%20successfully%20separated%20from%20the%20orbiter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan%202%20was%20launched%20from%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Sriharikota%20on%20July%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20revolving%20around%20the%20Earth's%20orbit%2C%20the%20spacecraft%20began%20its%20journey%20to%20the%20moon%20on%20August%2014.%20All%20manoeuvres%20were%20carried%20out%20to%20perfection%20until%20the%20last%20few%20minutes%20of%20descent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20saw%20all%20of%20India%20uniting%20in%20showing%20their%20support%20to%20the%20space%20agency%20and%20its%20scientists%2C%20who%20have%20said%20that%20the%20moon%20mission%20has%20accomplished%20at%20least%2090%20to%2095%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20objectives%20despite%20the%20severance%20of%20communication%20with%20the%20lander.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692789480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fmhgajpmo_vikram-lander-animation-650_650x400_07_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-is-all-set-to-make-history-a-look-at-what-went-wrong-with-chandrayaan-2-4322398%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20India%20will%20become%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20make%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20Moon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-is-all-set-to-make-history-a-look-at-what-went-wrong-with-chandrayaan-2-4322398%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-is-all-set