ainstream%20media%20has%20largely%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20demonstrations%20by%20farmers%20and%20their%20demands.%20Now%2C%20even%20small%20independent%20platforms%20such%20as%20Gaon-Savera%20that%20take%20a%20pro%20farmers%20and%20pro%20people%20stand%20are%20being%20targeted.%20Along%20with%20Gaon%20Savera%2C%20the%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20many%20farmer%20leaders%20have%20also%20been%20frozen%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20also%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20freezing%20of%20the%20website%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Srinagar-based%20news%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%20that%20the%20Kashmir%20website%E2%80%99s%20editor%20Fahad%20Shah%20had%20already%20been%20arrested%20in%20February%202022%2C%20and%20had%20been%20charged%20under%20UAPA%2C%20and%20languishes%20in%20jail.%20A%20former%20trainee%20reporter%20Sajad%20Gul%20is%20in%20a%20jail%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClosing%20down%20news%20portals%2C%20YouTube%20channels%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20is%20becoming%20a%20common%20tactic%20by%20governments%2C%20both%20in%20the%20states%20and%20at%20the%20centre.%20Prolonged%20internet%20bans%2C%20as%20in%20Manipur%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20are%20also%20becoming%20common.%20India%20is%20becoming%20infamous%20as%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20capital%20of%20the%20world%2C%20with%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20deliberate%20disruptions%20of%20the%20internet.%20The%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20calls%20for%20an%20end%20to%20all%20such%20arbitrary%20practices%20that%20bode%20ill%20for%20a%20free%20media%20and%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20the%20press%20release%20is%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20registers%20its%20strong%20protest%20at%20the%20rep