er.com%2Fhashtag%2FSachinMeena%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SachinMeena%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSeemaHaider%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SeemaHaider%3C%2Fa%3E%20fasting%20today%20for%20the%20success%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChandrayaan3Landing%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Chandrayaan3Landing%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe%20praises%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20said%20she%20will%20break%20her%20fast%20only%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChandrayaan3%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Chandrayaan3%3C%2Fa%3E%20lands%20on%20the%20Moon%20successfully.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1Lec5Cn1Zs%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1Lec5Cn1Zs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shameela%20(%40shaikhshameela)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshaikhshameela%2Fstatus%2F1694243601948242268%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20she%20is%20seen%20with%20her%20hands%20folded%20in%20reverence%20before%20the%20Hindu%20deities'%20idols.%20She%20says%2C%20''Though%20my%20health%20is%20not%20in%20its%20best%20state%2C%20I%20am%20observing%20a%20fast%20with%20the%20hope%20for%20Chandrayaan-3's%20successful%20landing%20scheduled%20for%20this%20evening.%20This%20accomplishment%20holds%20great%20promise%20for%20India's%20future.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20am%20committed%20to%20sustaining%20my%20fast%20until%20its%20successful%20landing.%20I%20offer%20my%20prayers%20to%20deities%20such%20as%20Radhe%20Krishna%2C%20in%20whom%20I%20place%20deep%20faith%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Shri%20Ram%20and%20all%20other%20revered%20Gods%20and%20Goddesses%2C%20seeking%20the%20triumph%20of%20Chandrayaan-3.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20''Our%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20worked%20hard%20for%20this%20project.%20The%20successful%20landing%20of%20Chandrayaan%C2%A0will%20raise%20India's%20name%20globally.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mrs.%20Haider%20was%20seen%20hoisting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseema-haider-pak-woman-who-came-to-india-hoists-tricolour-and-heres-what-anju-did-4297946%5C%22%3EIndian%20flag%20with%20her%20family%20in%20Noida%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0ahead%20of%20India's%2077th%20Independence%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Haider%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Sindh%20province%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20Sachin%20Meena%2C%2022%2C%C2%A0%20while%20playing%20the%20online%20game%20PUBG%20in%202019-20%20and%20eventually%2C%20the%20two%20talked%20over%20Whatsapp%20and%20Instagram%20before%20falling%20in%20love%20with%20each%20other.%C2%A0She%20entered%20India%20illegally%20along%20with%20her%20four%20children%20on%20a%20bus%20via%20Pakistan%20on%20May%2013%20and%20was%20arrested.%20However%2C%20she%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20a%20local%20court%20on%20July%207.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20now%20lives%20in%20the%20Rabupura%20area%20of%20Greater%20Noida%2C%20near%20Delhi%2C%20where%20he%20runs%20a%20provision%20store%2C%20according%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692786120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fs1fk5d8o_pakistani-woman_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fnoida-video-of-pak-woman-praying-for-successful-landing-of-chandrayaan-3-goes-viral-4322144%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seema%20Haider%2C%20who%20now%20lives%20in%20Noida%20with%20Sachin%20Meena%2C%20revealed%20that%20she%20has%20observed%20a%20fast%20for%20Chandrayaan-3's%20successful%20landing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fnoida-video-of-pak-woman-praying-for-successful-landing-of-chan