%3E%20But%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20Leonard%20Bernstein%2C%20he%20also%20did%20something%20that%20most%20people%20aren%E2%80%99t%20aware%20of%2C%20he%20played%20the%20violin%20in%20the%20all%20India%20Radio%20famous%20signature%20tune.%20Most%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20remember%20that%20signature%20tune%2C%20you%20probably%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EZM%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20They%20still%20play.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20tell%20you%2C%20I%20went%20with%20my%20wife%20and%20my%20children%20to%20Amarnath%20on%20a%20yatra%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20in%20the%20early%2070s%20and%20going%20to%20Amarnath%20we%20were%20in%20a%20Dak%20Bungalow%20on%20the%20way%20there%20about%2013%2C000%20feet%20high%2C%20I%20was%20sleeping%20at%20night%20and%20suddenly%20the%20people%20outside%20who%20were%20in%20charge%20of%20putting%20us%20on%20horses%20every%20day%20to%20take%20us%20to%20Amarnath%2C%20they%20switched%20off%20the%20radio%20just%20before%20that%20I%20heard%20my%20father%20play%20at%2013%2C000%20feet.%20I%20told%20my%20children%2C%20%E2%80%98This%20is%20your%20grandfather%20playing%20the%20violin%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20it%20still%20goes%20on%20and%20sometimes%20I%20tell%20people%20in%20America%20who%20all%20know%20this%20little%20tune.%20It%20was%20composed%20by%20a%20Czech%20Jewish%20composer%20called%20Walter%20Kaufman%2C%20who%20is%20a%20refugee%20and%20he%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20classical%20music%20at%20all%20India%20Radio%2C%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20chamber%20music%20with%20my%20father%2C%20and%20he%20composed%20that%20tune%20which%20is%20still%20used.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20haunting%20tune%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%20Once%20you%E2%80%99ve%20heard%20it%20stays%20in%20your%20head%20forever%2C%20yeah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EZM%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%E2%80%99m%20very%20glad%20you%20mentioned%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20You%20write%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20you%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20was%20wrapped%20up%20in%20and%20surrounded%20by%20music%20with%20my%20father%20practicing%20in%20the%20living%20room%20and%20with%20musical%20scores%20scattered%20all%20around%20the%20house%2C%20but%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20was%20Daddy%E2%80%99s%20gramophone%20and%20Daddy%E2%80%99s%20records.%E2%80%9D%20Is%20that%20right%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EZM%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20That%E2%80%99s%20right.%20That%E2%80%99s%20right.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20my%20orchestral%20education%20happened.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20went%20to%20Vienna%20when%20I%20was%2018%2C%20I%20knew%20a%20lot%20of%20music%20by%20ear.%20I%20had%20not%20studied%20it%20with%20a%20score%20in%20front%20of%20me%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20it%20by%20ear%20and%20then%20I%20heard%20the%20Great%20Vienna%20Philharmonic%20play%20the%20same%20music%2C%20which%20a%20sound%20I%20had%20never%20imagined%20existed%20because%20the%20orchestra%20I%20heard%20in%20Bombay%20was%20not%20of%20the%20same%20quality%2C%20of%20course.%20Today%20I%20must%20tell%20you%20I%20am%20very%20pleased%20with%20the%20Symphony%20of%20India%2C%20I%20am%20rehearsing%20with%20them%20every%20day.%20I%20hope%20some%20of%20you%20come%20to%20the%20concert.%20But%20they%20are%20playing%20beautifully%2C%20they%20have%20a%20very%20good%20standard%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20many%20Indians%20are%20in%20the%20orchestra%2C%20not%20too%20many%2C%20but%20they%20are%20Russian-speaking%2C%20Spanish-speaking%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20they%20play%20very%20well%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20very%20pleased.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Tell%20me%20about%20those%20days%20when%20you%20taught%20yourself%20music%20and%20the%20love%20of%20music%20that%20came%20with%20it%2C%20listening%20to%20records.%20Who%20chose%20the%20records%20that%20you%20list