%20Sharma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fwill-incorporate-rules-regulate-bad-words-vulgar-language-social-media-platforms-central-government-delhi-high-court%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20August%2017%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20examined%20the%20status%20report%20filed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20observed%20that%20because%20it%20is%20a%20policy%20decision%2C%20it%20is%20sufficient%20compliance%20of%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Court.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Court%20has%20been%20assured%20that%20the%20concerns%20of%20this%20Court%20expressed%20through%20the%20said%20judgment%20will%20be%20incorporated%20in%20the%20future%20rules%20and%20regulations%20which%20will%20be%20shortly%20undertaken.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20March%206%2C%20the%20court%20had%20severely%20criticised%20the%20web%20series%20and%20its%20use%20of%20profane%20language.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fwill-incorporate-rules-regulate-bad-words-vulgar-language-social-media-platforms-central-government-delhi-high-court%5C%22%3Erefusing%20to%20quash%20the%20FIR%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20actors%20and%20makers%20of%20the%20show%2C%20the%20court%20had%20directed%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20take%20steps%20for%20enforcing%20stricter%20application%20of%20its%20IT%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%2C%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FIR%20alleged%20that%20Episode%205%20of%20Season%201%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECollege%20Romance%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eshowcased%20indecent%20representation%20or%20obscene%20portrayal%20of%20girls%20or%20women%20in%20the%20worst%20form%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fwill-regulate-use-vulgar-language-social-media-p