Fhow-couple-quit-city-life-to-build-sustainable-homestay-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esentimental%20value%20of%20the%20home%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecompelled%20them%20to%20choose%20the%20first%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%E2%80%99re%20so%20glad%20we%20did%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20simple%20idea%20taking%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20restore%20the%20place%2C%20they%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20thought%20of%20converting%20it%20into%20a%20homestay.%20The%20inspiration%20came%20after%20Susmitha%20read%20an%20article%20in%202000%20about%20the%20emergence%20of%20%E2%80%98homestay%20culture%E2%80%99%20in%20Coorg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20why%20not%20Chikmagalur%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20thought.%20The%20city%20boasted%20of%20forests%2C%20waterfalls%2C%20and%20beautiful%20grasslands%2C%20all%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20luscious%20Western%20Ghats.%20The%20couple%20wanted%20the%20city%20to%20be%20known%20on%20the%20world-map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20heritage%20home%20offers%20bird%20watching%2C%20trekking%2C%20hiking%2C%20cycling%20and%20more%20to%20all%20adventure%20lovers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-300x285.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-500x474.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-768x729.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-1536x1457.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-150x142.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327706%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221518%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20heritage%20home%20offers%20bird%20watching%2C%20trekking%2C%20hiking%2C%20cycling%20and%20more%20to%20all%20adventure%20lovers%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Susmitha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20their%20very%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298965%2Fdelhi-professiors-turn-traditional-houses-into-homestays-boost-sustainable-tourism-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperience%20of%20hosting%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20say%20it%20was%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Eve%20in%202002%20that%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20turning%20point%20of%20their%20story.%20Intent%20on%20helping%20their%20friends%20find%20a%20getaway%20where%20they%20could%20ring%20in%20the%20new%20year%20in%20style%2C%20Susmitha%20and%20Shreedev%20offered%20them%20their%20very%20own%20recently-revamped%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20days%20that%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20friends%20spent%20at%20Woodway%20were%20the%20loveliest%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20This%20was%20encouraging%20news%20for%20the%20couple%20who%20had%20long%20since%20ruminated%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20welcoming%20guests%20into%20the%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Woodway%20Heritage%20Bungalow%20is%20almost%20always%20booked%20to%20capacity%20and%20those%20who%20leave%20its%20premises%20do%20so%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20return.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5