ucation)%20as%20technology%20is%20our%20future.%20If%20these%20students%20do%20not%20adapt%20to%20digital%20methods%2C%20chances%20are%20that%20they%20miss%20out%20on%20good%20opportunities.%20With%20Muskaan%20Dreams%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20bring%20smiles%20to%20these%20children%20and%20help%20them%20fulfil%20their%20dreams%20of%20a%20better%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2031-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202017%2C%20the%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government%20schools%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98When%20I%20took%20a%20stand%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20farmer%20family%20in%20rural%20Gwalior%2C%20Abhishek%20developed%20an%20interest%20in%20teaching%20underprivileged%20children%20during%20his%20college%20days.%20In%202013%2C%20while%20studying%20engineering%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20he%20started%20devoting%20his%20weekends%20to%20teaching%20children%20in%20government-run%20shelter%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20my%20classmates%20going%20to%20teach%20students%20in%20shelter%20homes.%20I%20went%20along%20with%20her%20and%20saw%20how%20such%20children%20are%20deprived%20of%20education.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20children%20of%20single%20parents%20and%20from%20tribal%20or%20rural%20backgrounds.%20Coming%20from%20a%20rural%20background%2C%20I%20started%20connecting%20with%20them%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20teach%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20years%2C%20they%20formed%20a%20group%20of%20200%20volunteers%20and%20expanded%20their%20reach%20to%20Bhopal%20and%20Indore%20as%20well.%20By%20now%2C%20this%20was%20no%20more%20a%20weekend%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%