et%20contains%20the%20most.%20So%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20buying%20biscuits%2C%20the%20first%20three%20ingredients%20usually%20will%20be%20maida%20(refined%20wheat%20flour)%2C%20palm%20oil%20and%20sugar%E2%80%9D%20says%20Revant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuy%20items%20that%20have%20less%20than%20five%20ingredients%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTry%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20products%20that%20have%20more%20than%20five%20ingredients.%20As%20the%20ingredient%20list%20increases%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20inversely%20proportional%20to%20the%20nutritional%20benefits.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAvoid%20products%20that%20have%20complicated%20ingredients%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20recognise%20or%20pronounce%20ingredients%20in%20a%20product%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20good%20for%20you.%20Buy%20the%20product%20in%20which%20you%20can%20understand%20the%20ingredient%2C%20like%20something%20that%20says%20dates%2C%20peanuts%2C%20milk%2C%20etc.%20If%20something%20has%20ingredients%20like%20maltodextrin%2C%20anti-caking%20agent%2C%20technical%20chemicals%2C%20stay%20away%20from%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuy%20items%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20list%20sugar%20in%20the%20first%205-6%20ingredients%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSteer%20clear%20of%20products%20that%20have%20sugar%20listed%20first%20or%20second.%20Those%20products%20are%20basically%20just%20sugar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGo%20for%20the%20slightly%20healthier%20options%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20idea%20is%20to%20make%20healthier%20choices.%20Instead%20of%20going%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Emaida%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebiscuit%2C%20