href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298712%2Fiim-graduate-citygreens-hydroponics-startup-trains-farmers-increase-earnings%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20used%20in%20hydroponics%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20found%20it%20very%20intriguing.%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20back%20to%20India%20and%20develop%20our%20own%20hydroponics%20system.%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20university%20and%20told%20them%20about%20my%20idea%20of%20developing%20a%20Hybrid%20Hydroponics%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Dr%20Sethi%20nearly%20five%20years%20to%20fully%20develop%20the%20HHT%20system%20and%20grow%20vegetables%20using%20it%2C%20and%20another%20five%20to%20get%20the%20patent%20rights%2C%20which%20he%20and%20PAU%20received%20in%20November%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20HHT%20and%20how%20does%20it%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20types%20of%20hydroponics%20%E2%80%94%20water-based%20and%20substrate-based.%20Dr%20Sethi%E2%80%99s%20hybrid%20technology%20merges%20the%20two%20to%20use%20the%20best%20of%20both%20technologies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20seed%20money%20of%20Rs%205%2C00%2C000%20from%20the%20university%2C%20I%20started%20my%20research%20on%20developing%20the%20technology.%20We%20developed%20a%20small%20greenhouse%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20250%20plants.%20It%20took%20me%20nearly%20two%20years%20to%20fully%20develop%20the%20technology%20and%20I%20tested%20it%20for%20another%20three%20years%20before%20applying%20for%20a%20patent%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20took%20a%20few%20hits%20and%20misses%20to%20become%20what%20it%20is%20today%2C%20notes%20Dr%20Sethi.%20While%20the%20concept%20of%20soil-less%20farming%20is%20not%20unknown%20to%20us%2C%20what%20he%20noticed%20was%20that%20the%20technology%20uses%20water%20from%20reservoirs%20and%20passes%20it%20to%20the%20pots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20that%20was%20not%20taken%20by%20the%20plants%20would%20go%20to%20waste.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Hybrid%20Hydroponics%20Technology%2C%20we%20save%20this%20water%20by%20using%20the%20technique%20of%20recirculation.%20We%20developed%20a%20porous%20plate%20between%20the%20pots.%20The%20lower%20part%20of%20the%20pot%20contains%20the%20shallow%20water%20pond%20and%20the%20upper%20part%20of%20the%20pot%20carries%20the%20substrate.%20The%20plate%20between%20the%20two%20is%20the%20innovation%20as%20it%20carries%20equivalent%20pressure%20at%20both%20the%20upper%20and%20lower%20end%20of%20the%20pot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20allows%20the%20roots%20to%20breathe%20and%20grow%2C%20and%20from%20the%20top%2C%20they%20would%20get%20ample%20oxygen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20recirculation%20mode%2C%20we%20could%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247233%2Fbori-bandh-check-dam-ajay-sharma-sewa-welfare-society-khunti-jharkhand-water-shortage-water-conservation-agriculture-volunteer-work-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20about%2090%25%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20allow%20even%20a%20drop%20to%20go%20to%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-2-1692278332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20took%20five%20years%20of%20research%20for%20Dr%20Sethi%20to%20develop%20the%20technology.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-2-1692278332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-2-1692278332-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-2-1692278332-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-2-1692278332-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-2-1692278332-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327484%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sethi%20developed%20India%E2%80%99s%20Hybrid%20Hydroponics%20Technology.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20V%20P%20Sethi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sethi%20also%20sprays%20the%20required%20minerals%20and%20nutrients%20on%20the%20plants%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20fruit%20is%20the%20best%20in%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20newly-developed%20technology%20underwent%20a%20rigorous%20two-year%20testing%20phase%20by%20cultivating%20cucumber%2C%20tomato%2C%20and%20capsicum%20crops.%20Through%20this%20experimentation%2C%20it%20was%20established%20that%20the%20technology%20accelerated%20growth%20and%20yielded%20higher%20produce%20compared%20to%20prevalent%20pot-based%20systems%20like%20the%20bato%20bucket%20(inspired%20by%20Dutch%20technology)%20and%20grow%20bag-based%20systems%20(non-recirculation%20type%2C%20inspired%20by%20Israeli%20technology)%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20soilless%20cultivation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20method%20is%20not%20labour%20intensive%20like%20traditional%20farming%20as%20it%20is%20fully%20automatic.%20We%20have%20timers%20that%20are%20set%20in%20advance%20that%20provide%20and%20sprinkle%20required%20nutrients%20according%20to%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20requirements.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20it%20accessible%20for%20local%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20few%20arguments%20that%20Dr%20Sethi%20presented%20on%20the%20need%20for%20such%20a%20technology%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20important%20reason%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20barren%20land%20in%20India%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20this%20purpose.%20Besides%2C%20this%20technology%20allows%20farmers%20and%20gardeners%20to%20grow%20food%20anywhere%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20closed%20room%20to%20a%20small%20terrace%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20also%20generate%20employment%20in%20the%20country.%20Right%20from%20a%20homemaker%20with%20a%20spare%20room%20in%20her%20house%20to%20an%20unemployed%20youth%2C%20anyone%20can%20easily%20use%20the%20technology%20to%20grow%20plants%20with%20a%20little%20training.%20They%20can%20consume%20it%20and%20sell%20the%20excess%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20why%20Dr%20Sethi%20thinks%20the%20technology%20is%20important%20is%20that%20it%20saves%20water.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20recirculation%20mode%2C%20with%20the%20use%20of%20HHT%2C%20we%20can%20save%20about%2060%20to%2090%25%20water%20depending%20on%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20making%20it%20accessible%20to%20the%20local%20farmers%2C%20he%20says%20that%20there%20are%20plans%20underway.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-4-1692279060.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Using%20HHT%2C%20the%20university%20has%20grown%20vegetables%20like%20tomatoes%2C%20cherry%20tomatoes%2C%20cucumber%2C%20bell%20pepper%20and%20capsicum%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-4-1692279060.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-4-1692279060-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-4-1692279060-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A